data.description: WELCOME to small town living in Valparaiso, NE! Conveniently located on a corner lot next to parks and local businesses, this home has all the perks of being close to Lincoln while still being nestled in a small community! A very rare find, this house has all the original charm combined with plenty of updates; it is move in-ready and waiting for its next buyer!  Fall in love with a new fully fenced in yard, surrounded by large trees, with a spacious front porch and new rock driveway! Located right next to the house is a large outbuilding to keep all of your toys in, or could be used as a workshop for the right buyer.  Come inside this gorgeous 2-Story home and you'll find 5 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Enjoy your mornings at a coffee bar in the dining room, while doing laundry on the main floor near your enclosed porch. Or go downstairs in the basement to complete your projects by the wetbar. *Transferrable warranty and propane levels to new buyer!* Home being sold AS-IS, schedule today!
